
Most people are unaware that there is no such thing as a "Family" coat  of arms - they are only given to individuals. You will find a very interesting article on the Coat of Arms subject in the Watkins Family Newsletter, February, 2004 issue.
You can download the Newsletter at the following link:http://www.watkinsfhs.net/newsletter/newletters_2004.shtml
